tokens.name: Gold Compass Medallion #5
tokens.description: Gold medallions were awarded to the command and control members of Operation Compass. Archivists are tasked with researching, cataloging, and maintaining all written materials. Archivists in Operation Compass were of different ranks, Master, Adept, Journeyman, and Apprentice.
